but he's definitely not Santa.

01:09:03.087 --> 01:09:03.756
Augustus.

01:09:05.383 --> 01:09:05.863
Hello.

01:09:07.716 --> 01:09:11.158
l'm Eli, Santa's head elf,
and this is Eddy.

01:09:13.849 --> 01:09:15.966
Great, now l'm seeing elves.

01:09:18.520 --> 01:09:21.492
What are you guys,
from the North Pole?

01:09:22.857 --> 01:09:23.817
Yes, we are.

01:09:27.613 --> 01:09:29.729
You just talked, didn't you?

01:09:30.156 --> 01:09:32.450
Well, sure l did. l'm an elf dog.

01:09:32.451 --> 01:09:35.183
Well, Gus.
You finally have lost it.

01:09:41.877 --> 01:09:45.046
