- That explains the beard.

01:09:45.046 --> 01:09:47.921
The magic of Santa's cystal
has been changing you.

01:09:47.923 --> 01:09:52.303
- Where did you get this?
- This old guy, he got hit by a taxi.

01:09:52.304 --> 01:09:55.339
He gave me his suitcase
and this cystal.

01:09:58.935 --> 01:09:59.227
No?

01:10:01.230 --> 01:10:05.046
l took both of them,
but l feel terrible about it.

01:10:08.862 --> 01:10:09.404
Eddy...

01:10:11.447 --> 01:10:13.762
