01:10:36.139 --> 01:10:37.890
Eli? Eddy, is that you?

01:10:38.850 --> 01:10:41.936
lt most certainly is.
We're here to rescue you all!

01:10:41.937 --> 01:10:44.429
Hallelujah! We've been so worried.

